scripts.build:android: npm run mkdist && react-native bundle --entry-file index.js --platform android --dev true --bundle-output dist/main.android.jsbundle --assets-dest dist && react-native build-android --extra-params "--no-daemon --console=plain -PreactNativeArchitectures=arm64-v8a"
scripts.build:ios: npm run mkdist && react-native bundle --entry-file index.js --platform ios --dev true --bundle-output dist/main.ios.jsbundle --assets-dest dist && react-native build-ios --scheme EngleLlmExample --mode Release --extra-params "-sdk iphoneos -allowProvisioningUpdates CC=clang CPLUSPLUS=clang++ LD=clang LDPLUSPLUS=clang++ GCC_OPTIMIZATION_LEVEL=0 GCC_PRECOMPILE_PREFIX_HEADER=YES ASSETCATALOG_COMPILER_OPTIMIZATION=time DEBUG_INFORMATION_FORMAT=dwarf COMPILER_INDEX_STORE_ENABLE=NO CODE_SIGN_IDENTITY='' CODE_SIGNING_REQUIRED=NO CODE_SIGN_ENTITLEMENTS='' CODE_SIGNING_ALLOWED=NO"
scripts.build:iossimulator: npm run mkdist && react-native bundle --entry-file index.js --platform ios --dev true --bundle-output dist/main.ios.jsbundle --assets-dest dist && react-native build-ios --scheme EngleLlmExample --mode Debug --extra-params "-sdk iphonesimulator -allowProvisioningUpdates CC=clang CPLUSPLUS=clang++ LD=clang LDPLUSPLUS=clang++ GCC_OPTIMIZATION_LEVEL=0 GCC_PRECOMPILE_PREFIX_HEADER=YES ASSETCATALOG_COMPILER_OPTIMIZATION=time DEBUG_INFORMATION_FORMAT=dwarf COMPILER_INDEX_STORE_ENABLE=NO CODE_SIGN_IDENTITY='' CODE_SIGNING_REQUIRED=NO CODE_SIGN_ENTITLEMENTS='' CODE_SIGNING_ALLOWED=NO"
